headline: The Top S&P 500 Stock of 2024 (So Far) Isn't Nvidia. Here's Where History Says the Soaring Stock Is Headed in 2025.
summary: On Nov. 20, Nvidia reported financial results for its fiscal 2025 third quarter, showing stunning 94% year-over-year revenue growth.  The business is absolutely booming, and so is the stock price.  As of this writing, Nvidia stock is up close to 200% year to date.
